                "invention-title": [
                    "Low-carbon park optimal configuration method and system",
                    "一种低碳园区优化配置方法和系统"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses an optimal configuration method and system for a low-carbon park, electric energy substitution and a stepped carbon transaction mechanism are considered, a double-layer planning model is constructed, the upper-layer model takes the minimum comprehensive cost as a target, and the investment operation cost of carbon capture equipment, an electrolytic cell, a hydrogen storage tank, a hydrogen fuel cell, a methane reactor and cogeneration equipment is considered; the lower-layer model aims at minimizing the operation cost, considers the carbon transaction cost and the operation cost of equipment such as carbon capture equipment, converts the lower-layer model into a constraint condition of the upper-layer model, and solves the constraint condition to obtain an optimal low-carbon operation scheme of the park comprehensive energy operation system; therefore, the system achieves the purpose of reducing the cost and the carbon emission at the same time, and solves the technical problems that the existing park comprehensive energy planning mainly focuses on the consumption of wind and light and the economical efficiency of system operation, does not consider the low-carbon economic operation of the comprehensive energy system, and is not beneficial to the sustainable development of the park."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了一种低碳园区优化配置方法和系统，考虑了电能替代和阶梯式碳交易机制，构建了双层规划模型，上层模型以综合成本最小为目标，考虑了碳捕集设备、电解槽、储氢罐、氢燃料电池、甲烷反应器和热电联产设备的投资运行成本；下层模型使得运行成本最小为目标，考虑了碳交易成本、碳捕集设备等设备的运行成本，将下层模型转换为上层模型的约束条件并进行求解，得到园区综合能源运行系统的最优低碳运行方案，从而使得系统同时达到降低成本与碳排放量的目的，解决了现有的园区综合能源规划主要关注风光的消纳与系统运行的经济性，未考虑到综合能源系统的低碳经济运行，不利于园区的可持续发展的技术问题。"
                }
            ]
